SummaryEnglish: Xiao He is a handsome medical student who is also a popular online power player. One day, he manages to defeat the most wanted criminal on the server, the famous bandit Tao Zhi Yao Yao, but is surprised to discover that she is actually Wei Sheng Xin Yue, the former first female e-sports player. Why would she have changed her name and become a bandit? Offline, the two meet by mistake on several occasions without knowing who they really are. What will happen when they finally meet again on the e-sports scene?
